### Current Contents.
# Current Version 1.0.1

Style & Layout:

- Bootrap
- Bulma Css
- 
Store:
- Homepage
- Categories
- Navbar
- Footer
- Sidebar
Payment Choices
- Stripe
- Paypal
- payment refund
- Coupon Applied
Product Items:
- upload from admin

### Roadmap to version 1.0.2.

